{"tid":2148024,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"住緊居屋嘅你，有冇比我啲琴聲嘈到？","createTime":"2020-08-09T15:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T02:16:19.000Z","uid":309398,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"231e8192f3cc915f324b52de8f69562cd6ad7f39","tid":2148024,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:52:06.000Z","msg":"十幾年前萬幾蚊買咗個Yamaha直身琴，由幼稚園彈到依家讀大學，近年隨著水平越嚟越高，開始覺得個琴虧，好嘈（彈三角彈same touch different output）<br />\n<br />\n依家練琴前會刪細啲個窗，或開冷氣，想問你住隔離其實有冇被我嘈到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4029da6aaa6daa9281b222b059122154221ad9a4","tid":2148024,"uid":314136,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:53:25.000Z","msg":"原來就係你<br />\n彈撚到走嗮音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4befd9389b762af07c87eafb74aaafee871c70d0","tid":2148024,"uid":109050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"屌你係咪我對面屋,又係三角琴,成日打開度門彈琴,其實真係好撚嘈下"},{"pid":"2b4ac17c25bc08295aa56c9453f6910b804cbf4c","tid":2148024,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4029da6aaa6daa9281b222b059122154221ad9a4","tid":2148024,"uid":314136,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:53:25.000Z","msg":"原來就係你<br />\n彈撚到走嗮音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"近排先tune 過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我彈得幾好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b55dca8b1d45574b045906ce2489f0b9bc9897","tid":2148024,"uid":169198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"中午12點前 同夜晚6點後唔好彈ok?"},{"pid":"37214b6ca1c2fe6e1c5c5ec9a9eb50cc40080eeb","tid":2148024,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score